flowchart TD
    Trigger{Delivery source} -- Order ready --> Create[Admin creates delivery<br/>for the order]
    Trigger -- Subscription cycle due --> Create2[System/admin creates delivery<br/>for the cycle]
    Create --> Assign
    Create2 --> Assign

    Assign[Admin assigns a rider] --> NotiR[Notify rider: new delivery]
    NotiR --> RiderView[Rider opens 'My Deliveries'<br/>sees only assigned]
    RiderView --> Pick[Rider picks up items]
    Pick --> OFD[Mark Out for delivery]
    OFD --> NotiC1[Notify customer: on the way]
    NotiC1 --> Attempt{Delivery attempt}

    Attempt -- Success --> Proof[Mark Delivered<br/>upload proof photo + notes]
    Proof --> Sync[Order status -> Delivered]
    Sync --> NotiC2[Notify customer: delivered]
    NotiC2 --> Review[Customer can now review] --> End([Delivered])

    Attempt -- Failed --> Fail[Mark Failed + reason]
    Fail --> Reassign{Admin action}
    Reassign -- Reassign --> Assign
    Reassign -- Retry later --> RiderView
